tion in a certain region of the invariant subspace\nassociated with slow modes displays some extended predictability, as reflected\nby the oscillatory behavior of the error for the atmospheric variables at long\nlead times.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Dec 2014 20:08:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Jul 2015 10:36:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 27 Aug 2015 10:25:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-28"}
