ut. This formalism allows direct definitions of all the invariants we\nconsider in terms of the functional calculus of the Dirac operator and enables\nus to give concise proofs of the product formulas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Dec 2014 21:14:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Aug 2015 20:42:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 4 Dec 2015 17:31:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-15"}
