f\nthose observed in binary hard spherical particles. Therefore, our results\nsuggest a universal mechanism for the influence of size disparity and mixture's\ncomposition on the structural relaxation in both isotropic and anisotropic\nparticle systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Dec 2014 21:52:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-03"}
